title: Outback Farm
overview: Outback Farm is an exiting new TV series that aims to give the audience a glimp into the lives of the Aussies that live and work on stations and farms in the Outback.Outback Farm will continue the adventures of the water drilling Haigh family from Outback Truckers. The series follows Danyelle and Anthony and their two kids, Theo and Heath, who are about to embark on their greatest Outback adventure yet. In the harsh desert wilderness of the Northern Territory (NT), the Haigh family is risking it all. They've moved thousands of kilometres from their support network of friends and family in Queensland, to buy a $7 million farm in the dead heart of Australia, 200km from Alice Springs.
